   195→   *   <li><b>Taxonomy axioms</b>: SubClassOf axioms referencing named individuals (enum values)</li>
   196→   *   <li><b>SubClass axioms</b>: Direct SubClassOf axioms for the analyzed class</li>
   197→   *   <li><b>SuperClass axioms</b>: Inherited axioms from the class hierarchy</li>
